sequenceDiagram
    participant BUYER as Buyer
    participant SELL as Seller
    participant DALP as DALP Settlement
    participant CBS as Core Banking
    participant AUDIT as Audit Log
    participant REG as Regulator Feed

    BUYER->>DALP: Initiate settlement instruction
    SELL->>DALP: Confirm asset delivery
    DALP->>DALP: Pre-settlement compliance check
    DALP->>DALP: Lock asset + cash legs
    DALP->>CBS: Debit / credit notification
    CBS-->>DALP: Confirmation
    DALP->>DALP: Atomic execution (DVP)
    DALP-->>BUYER: Settlement confirmed
    DALP-->>SELL: Settlement confirmed
    DALP->>AUDIT: Immutable settlement record
    DALP->>REG: Regulatory reporting event (CBE format)
